attributes.description: Trend Micro Vision One Network Activity Events Overview.

params.markdown:
**Overview**

This dashboard offers a unified view of network-focused endpoint events, helping security teams quickly identify abnormal or high-volume activity. It highlights the top source and destination IPs to uncover suspicious connections or potential attack origins. Event trends over time reveal spikes, anomalies, and evolving patterns. Additional breakdowns by host OS, user name, and hostname provide context on which systems or identities are most impacted. The Top Rule Category chart further surfaces dominant detection types, enabling faster triage and prioritization. Together, these insights strengthen visibility and support proactive threat investigation.
